## Pioneer Camp

**Entering Grades 1–2**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Pioneer Camp"] /%}

**June 4–5** — $100

A one-night day camp experience designed just for our youngest campers! Pioneer Camp gives grades 1–2 a fun, safe introduction to Otyokwah with camp games, cabin time, and community — the perfect first step into the full camp experience.

{% ctaButton
