## Junior Camp

**Entering Grades 3–5**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Junior 1", "Junior 2"] /%}

**Junior Camp 1**: June 14–19 | **Junior Camp 2**: July 5–10

$390 early bird / $440 regular

Full-week adventure for elementary students! Junior Campers enjoy a full schedule — worship, Bible study, climbing the wall, zip line thrills, The Blob, kayaking, archery, disc golf, campfire gatherings, and more — all while building friendships and mentor relationships.

{% ctaButton
   label="Register Now"
   href="https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=1342&campcode=OTY"
   variant="inverse"
   size="lg"
   textColor="accent" /%}
{% /gridSquare %}

