## Jr. High Camp

**Entering Grades 6–8**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Jr. High 1", "Jr. High 2"] /%}

**Jr. High Camp 1**: June 7–12 | **Jr. High Camp 2**: July 12–17

$390 early bird / $440 regular

A week of growth and exploration for middle school students! Jr. High Campers are challenged to grow in faith through group discussions, Bible study, and chapel messages — all while conquering the climbing wall, flying down the zip line, hitting The Blob, paddling kayaks, and building lasting friendships.

{% ctaButton
   label="Register Now"
