## Sr. High Camp

**Entering Grades 9–12**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Sr. High"] /%}

**June 21–26** — $390 early bird / $440 regular

Our summer session for high school students! Sr. High campers dive into rich community, awesome activities like the climbing wall, zip line, disc golf, kayaking, and archery, and are equipped to engage Jesus Christ through Scripture and worship around the campfire.

